            <h2>Why is SchoolPost different?</h2>
            <p class="intro-text">SchoolPost is much more than an electronic broadcast system - it is an inclusive service which parents, staff and pupils can engage with to dramatically improve communication. It integrates with existing systems and data so requires very little work to set up and maintain.</p>
            <p>The integral online 'mailbox' makes it easy for parents to keep track of all their communication in one place, and the online forms can save your admin staff significant time collating replies - as well as improving response times by making it easy for parents.</p>
            <p>You can also use SchoolPost to securely publish reports, assessments and exam results online, and there is an optional 'documents by category' area for reference materials like policies and standard forms.</p>
